Package com.amplifyframework.datastore.syncengine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LastSyncMetadata
    Metadata about the last time that a model class was sync'd with AppSync backend.
    MutationQueue
    The MutationQueue is a LinkedHashMap like container , the goal of using this container is to achieve O(1) time complexity for both getting a PendingMutation and update an existing mutation with valid id.
    NetworkStatusMonitor
    This class is responsible for monitoring the reachability of the remote API by listening to certain events emitted by the API plugin.
    Orchestrator
    Synchronizes changed data between the LocalStorageAdapter and AppSync.
    OutboxMutationEvent<M extends Model>
    Event payload for the DataStoreChannelEventName.OUTBOX_MUTATION_ENQUEUED event and DataStoreChannelEventName.OUTBOX_MUTATION_PROCESSED event.
    OutboxMutationEvent.OutboxMutationEventElement<M extends Model>
    An element representing the data that changed in this outbox event.
    OutboxMutationFailedEvent<M extends Model>
    Event payload for the DataStoreChannelEventName.OUTBOX_MUTATION_FAILED event.
    PendingMutation<T extends Model>
    Models a change that is waiting to be uploaded to a remote system.
    PendingMutation.PersistentRecord
    Used for storing PendingMutations into a LocalStorageAdapter.
    RetryStrategy
    Class that defines inner classes and interfaces related to retry strategies.
    TimeBasedUuidTypeAdapter
    Adapter to serialize and deserialize TimeBasedUuid to and from JSON.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Orchestrator.State
    The current state of the Orchestrator.
    OutboxMutationFailedEvent.MutationErrorType
    Categorization of error types that caused a mutation publication to fail.
    SyncType
    Enum representing the type of initial sync.
